<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_360" id="179r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_360_r1l14">Graf Eymichein von 
<del rend="strikethrough">leiny </del> leymingen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_360_r1l15"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> vns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> vt <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> <expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Alcʒe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l16">vnd lawtern <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey worden . dıe gen wıldenſtein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l17">ſey <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> . darynne Jm ewr gnade gar fürderlich <expan>gevveſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l18">ſey . daʒ Jm der einteil wıdervvorden ſey . des wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l19">gnaden <expan>fleiſʒiklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l20"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> fürbaſmer ewr gnedig <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> beweiſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l22">wöllet / daʒ Jm dieſelb ſein habe 
<del rend="strikethrough">vollen </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_360_r1l21">vollen </ab></add> wıder werde </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l23">Als etc das wöllen etc </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_360_r1l24"><expan>Johan<ex>n</ex></expan> von Stein . <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> <expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_360_r1l25"><expan>mutand<ex>is</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_360" id="179r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Graf Eymichein von Leymingen</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat
                                                  <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> ut
                                                  <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>
<expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Alcze und Lawtern
                                                  <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey worden, die
                                                gen Wildenstein sey <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                                darynne im ewr gnade gar fürderlich
                                                  <expan>gewese<ex>n</ex></expan> sey, daz im der
                                                ein teil widerworden sey, des wir
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden
                                                  <expan>fleisziklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und
                                                  <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                                                  <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> fürbasmer ewr gnedig
                                                  <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> beweisen wöllet,
                                                daz im dieselb sein habe <add>vollen</add> wider
                                                werde. Als etc. Das wöllen etc.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>Johan<ex>n</ex></expan> von Stein
                            <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>
<expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan>
<expan>mutand<ex>is</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
